uot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;作为触摸板&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/2/24 /21147654/samsung-galaxy-buds-plus-review-wireless-earbuds-sound-quality-battery-life&quot;>;可连接翼尖&lt;/a>;。考虑到 FE 的绰号，这些功能和设计并不令人意外，因为三星通常将 FE 用于以较低价格提供其高端产品的许多功能的产品。 （&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22880297/samsung-galaxy-s21-fe-review-screen-battery-specs-price&quot;>;S...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/13/23871933/samsung-galaxy-buds-fe-user-manual-leak&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/13/23871933/samsung-galaxy-buds-fe-user-manual-leak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/13/23871933/samsung-galaxy-buds-fe-user-manual-leak</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-13T12:37:10-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-13T12:37:10-04:00</updated><title>如何预订 Apple 即将推出的 iPhone 15 机型</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iPhone 15 所有颜色的阵容。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7DO0W8aThiurbO-ekTntM-5KQ-g=/0x0:3840x2560/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72640127/Apple_iPhone_15_lineup_color_lineup_230912。 0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;iPhone 15 采用柔和色彩和黑色的小彩虹色。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DEMYII&quot;>;Apple &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23869728/apple-iphone-15-event-announcements-watch-ultra -airpods-pro-usb-c&quot;>;在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23862837/iphone-15- 上正式宣布新款 iPhone 15&lt;/a>; 系列event-apple-watch-ultra-airpods-usb-c&quot;>;Wonderlust 活动&lt;/a>;，将于 9 月 15 日开始预订，一周后于 9 月 22 日发货。与去年一样，有一个基准 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23870387/iphone-15-plus-hands-on-pictures-video-price&quot;>;iPhone 15&lt;/a>;，较大的 iPhone 15 Plus，以及一对名为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23859793/iphone-15-pro-max-hands-on-pictures-video-apple&quot;>; 的 Pro 型号iPhone 15 Pro 和 iPhone 15 Pro Max&lt;/a>;。不过，虽然 15 Pro 和 15 Pro Max 预计将采用新的 A17 Pro Bionic 芯片（标准 15 和 15 Plus 使用去年的 A16 Bionic），但这次的最大不同是 USB 接口的存在。 C 充电/数据端口以及所有新型号均配备动态岛。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;nV6wZC&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以在此处预订 Apple Watch Series 9 和 Watch Ultra 2 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/23862174/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;苹果 iPhone 15 活动：七大重大公告&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23869728/apple-iphone-15-event-announcements-watch-ultra-airpods-pro-usb-c&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;苹果是9 月 18 日发布 iOS 17 和 iPadOS 17&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23863224/ios-17-release-date-apple-iphone-15-announcement&quot; }]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;1YU5kp&quot;>;虽然我们仍然需要在即将到来的评测中看看所有这些新 iPhone 的表现如何，但早期采用者将有机会。 ..&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23859935/iphone-15-plus-pro-max-preorder-buy-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23859935/iphone-15-plus-pro-max-preorder-buy-price-release-date-apple" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23859935/iphone-15-plus-pro-max-preorder-buy-price-release-date-apple</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-13T12:32:04-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-13T12:32:04-04:00</updated><title>拜登政府批准拨款 1 亿美元来修复该国损坏的电动汽车充电器</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Electrify America 电动汽车充电站&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RN2TYREBLr-D5aF9LqnPWUrDES0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72643238/ahawkins_20210503_4551_0015.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Andrew Hawkins / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;2Tbayy&quot;>;电动车车主厌倦了经常损坏的情况美国混乱的充电体验即将得到联邦政府的救命稻草。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0pFY5s&quot;>;美国交通部授权拨款 1 亿美元，用于“维修和更换现有但无法运行的电动汽车 (EV) 充电基础设施”。该投资来自&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/2/10/22926969/electric-vehicle-ev-charging-network-biden-plan&quot;>;75亿美元的资金&lt;/ a>; 作为 2021 年两党基础设施​​法的一部分获得批准的电动汽车充电。该部门&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/9/14/23353562/biden-ev-charging-900-million-funding-highway&quot;>;已批准约 10 亿美元&lt;/a>;在美国主要高速公路沿线安装数千个新的电动汽车充电器。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;csWcwy&quot;>;损坏的电动汽车充电器仍然是电动汽车更广泛采用的主要障碍。它往往会损害拥有电动汽车的体验，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/16/23833337/ev-charging-unreliable-worsening-survey-jd-power&quot;>;正如许多电动汽车车主早些时候告诉 JD Power 的那样...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/13/23871857/ev-charger-broken -fix-biden-usdot-funding-infrastructure&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/13/23871857/ev-charger-broken-fix-biden-usdot-funding-infrastructure" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/13/23871857/ev-charger-broken-fix-biden-usdot-funding-infrastruct</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-13T12:30:21-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-13T12:30:21-04:00</updated><title>您可以在此处预订 Apple Watch Series 9 和 Watch Ultra 2</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Zw5CvXSaNecmlj6LQe-Dv2UU21c=/0x0:2175x1450/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /72639773/Apple_Watch_Series_9_and_Watch_Ultra_2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 即将推出的手表拥有更好的性能、新的超宽带芯片以及其他细微改进。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Ok9iJm&quot;>;又到了一年中的这个时候。在周二的 Wonderlust 活动中，苹果推出了许多新产品，包括传闻已久的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23859779/iphone-15-plus-usb -c-price-release-date-apple&quo